The paper describes a system that extracts knowledge from the web, which is a common task in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The system also stores the extracted data in a structured format, which is related to database systems (cs.DB). The paper also mentions the use of Linked Data principles, which is a topic in semantic web (cs.LG) and web science (cs.SI).
